Danish: En stærk harddisk med
indbygget CD-rom drev, netværkskort og
lydkort)» - I really would like to see
that!! It was also avilable in

        »PIC:Kollaps5.iff»














different colours. A harddisk sure is
an important part of a computer and is
placed inside the cabinet, but
